  "description" : "* Based on http://anidb.net/cr28670 [Kawahara Reki]`s light novel series Sword Art Online.\nThe world`s first full-dive VRMMO, Sword Art Online—known as SAO. What was meant to be a dream come true has instead transformed into a deadly game where dying in the virtual world means dying in reality.\nhttp://anidb.net/character/154565 [Emirun] and http://anidb.net/character/154566 [Rex], who once knew each other in the real world, reunite by chance within SAO. They join a scouting party to learn how to survive in this unforgiving world. One day, however, they encounter a mysterious PK (Player Killer) known only as the http://anidb.net/character/37273 [Black Swordsman]. When Emirun rushes to the scene, she finds Rex collapsed in despair, and the Black Swordsman standing over him. The one who wiped out their entire scouting party—was the Black Swordsman.\nDetermined to avenge their fallen comrades, Emirun and Rex seek out the legendary prodigy swordswoman http://anidb.net/character/37272 [Asuna], and begin intense training under her guidance. In a death game where even players turn against one another, what new beginning will these two reach at the end of their struggle…?\nSource: Official site\nNote: Bonus Movie included in the Ultimate Edition of the video game Sword Art Online: Echoes of Aincrad released on July 9, 2026. It received a exclusive theatrical screening on May 9, 2026.",
